by GromNaN at 2024-03-21T12:54:20Z

The list of autoconfigured attributes is in [`FrameworkExtension`](https://github.com/symfony/symfony/blob/7.1/src/Symfony/Bundle/FrameworkBundle/DependencyInjection/FrameworkExtension.php#L663)

- [x] `AsEventListener`
- [x] `AsController`
- [x] `AsRemoteEventConsumer`
- [x] `AsMessageHandler`
- [x] `AsTargetedValueResolver`
- [x] `AsSchedule`
- [x] `AsPeriodicTask`
- [x] `AsCronTask`
- [x] `Workflow\Attribute\AsAnnounceListener`
- [x] `Workflow\Attribute\AsCompletedListener`
- [x] `Workflow\Attribute\AsEnterListener`
- [x] `Workflow\Attribute\AsEnteredListener`
- [x] `Workflow\Attribute\AsGuardListener`
- [x] `Workflow\Attribute\AsLeaveListener`
- [x] `Workflow\Attribute\AsTransitionListener`

