by GromNaN at 2024-03-22T10:17:34Z

It will be also possible to remove the handling for all the `Workflow` attributes, since it duplicates `AsEventListener` handler.
https://github.com/symfony/symfony/blob/bff8e0889497f5e722681efda730d1f078848427/src/Symfony/Bundle/FrameworkBundle/DependencyInjection/FrameworkExtension.php#L1108-L1129

