by GromNaN at 2024-03-22T13:30:56Z

All the [internal attributes](https://github.com/symfony/symfony/pull/54365#issuecomment-2012212477) can be extended and we already have an [internal use-case with Workflow attributes](https://github.com/symfony/symfony/pull/54365#issuecomment-2014772039).

Ready for review.
